        { q: 'How much does pest control cost in Hyderabad?', a: 'Pest control costs in Hyderabad depend on the type of service, property size, and severity of infestation. We offer transparent pricing. Contact us for a free quote.' },
        { q: 'Do you provide same-day pest control service in Hyderabad?', a: 'Yes, we offer same-day pest control in Hyderabad for most treatments. Call us for emergency services.' },
        { q: 'Which areas in Hyderabad do you cover?', a: 'We cover all areas across Hyderabad and surrounding regions including residential, commercial, and industrial zones.' },
        { q: 'Is your pest control service safe for kids and pets in Hyderabad?', a: 'Yes! All treatments in Hyderabad use WHO-approved, government-certified, low-toxicity products that are safe for families, children, and pets.' },
        { q: 'How do I book pest control in Hyderabad?', a: 'Call us, WhatsApp us, or fill the online form above. We confirm appointments in Hyderabad within 30 minutes.' }
      ]; %>
